          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘的痴病又发了，必定又是宝二爷得罪了他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，姑娘，今日乃是饯花盛会，各房的奶奶姑娘，都在园里送春，等候姑娘前"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去，联诗饮酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉如不闻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炉烟如我瘦，辛苦未成灰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，各房的奶奶姑娘们在园子里送春，等姑娘前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么……送春？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去了么，到哪里去了，怎么不叫她回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去无言，叫我那里寻找？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春去消息谁知，除非问取黄鹂呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "紫鹃，安顿花锄，我要葬花去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面春风似剪，姑娘不去也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，你看花谢花飞一片片沾泥随水。想世间薄命的人儿，还不是同落花一样么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扫愁帚贮香囊花锄一柄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且到沁芳桥葬玉埋春。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们姑娘，跟宝玉自幼十分相爱。哪里晓得越相爱，越烦恼。年纪一天大似一"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天。据我想来，彼此既然真心相爱，就要彼此原谅，每日里牵愁惹恨，又何苦"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呢？正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两情只要能长久，岂在朝朝暮暮愁。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "林黛玉→紫娟",
          "turns": 6
        },
        {
          "edge": "紫娟→林黛玉",
          "turns": 5
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
