    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "林黛玉",
        "紫娟",
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨夜晚怨东风无端蹂躏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生宝玉。今日一来是赴饯花盛会，二来这几日林妹妹有些恼我，必然是小生"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这里扫残红独穿花径，"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此已是林妹妹葬花之所，你看梨花飘雪，柳絮飞棉，倘若林妹妹看见，必定"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉扫花，望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远望一女子，隐约行过花丛，好像是林妹妹来了，待我闪躲一旁，听她讲些什"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "隔林听燕语，掬水奠花魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "碧云天芳草地蜂愁蝶怨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是葬花之所。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个有心人替我扫了一堆花瓣在此？莫非是那宝……嗳，他哪里有这样细腻的"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "反二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "林黛玉把花锄无限凄怆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侬今葬花人笑痴，他年葬侬知是谁。一朝春尽红颜老，花落人亡两不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉在假山后偷窥，失声哭，衣兜中花撒落满地。林黛玉惊祝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是即狼心短……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉、贾宝玉同绕场，林黛玉欲行，贾宝玉止。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，不要走。且等我说完这一句话。大家撩开手就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝二爷有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有今日，何必当初？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当初怎么，今日又怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初妹妹与我，是怎样的要好，彼此一处长大，每日一同吃饭，一同玩耍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你休来骗我。你还是回去关上你的门罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，此话从何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚我到怡红院去，你为何闭门不理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪有此事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还说没有此事，我站在门外，脚也站酸了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真正没有此事。妹妹若不相信，待我对天盟誓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉、贾宝玉互视，同笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还不快快的起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，这你可相信了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大约是你家大丫头偷赖不来开门，也是有的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我回去教训她们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也应当教训教训。得罪了我，不要紧，倘若得罪了什么宝姑娘、贝姑娘，那还"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她又提起宝姐姐了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今日来此则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都只为收拾那残脂剩粉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，这香冢之旁，那堆花瓣，是你扫来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么知道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀。还是他有这细腻的心情呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他言不由我芳心辗转，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉、贾宝玉同叹。紫鹃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "紫娟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他们又是怎么样了？待我诳她回去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉做身段，林黛玉、紫娟同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "流水斜阳春去尽，独留青冢向黄昏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
